Package com.flipkart.bean

Class FlipFitGymOwner

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.bean.FlipFitUser
com.flipkart.bean.FlipFitGymOwner
public class FlipFitGymOwner extends FlipFitUser
Represents a gym owner in the FlipFit system. This class extends FlipFitUser and includes additional details specific to gym owners.
